<h2>Brief Description</h2>
<p>
The Smart Parking & Mobility Hub automates vehicle parking, slot detection, mobility guidance, 
and EV charging distribution. It integrates sensors, real-time maps, and autonomous shuttle routing 
to reduce traffic congestion and improve visitor convenience.
</p>

